{"tid":883284,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"是咁的，我老婆有左","createTime":"2018-10-30T17:08:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T17:25:03.000Z","uid":139089,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"09b919a3cc7b26d56d58b22d95b8e1e2bd1f931b","tid":883284,"uid":139089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T17:08:54.000Z","msg":"如果有留意車post 既咁多位ching <br />\n都知我前年結左婚<br />\n雖然一直都好鐘意小朋友，<br />\n但始終都係想過多兩三年，闖多幾年先<br />\n<br />\n本身我屋企環境唔錯既，老豆老母都有資產淨<br />\n而我老婆算係富家女，同我結婚之後先無司機接送<br />\n我自己就係出面打份工，叫做有d成績<br />\n夠我買一兩架跑車玩下<br />\n<br />\n但係正當我老婆忽然同我講有左，我真係慌多過開心<br />\n一直我既打算都係專心做多幾年野，搵夠錢，真係生活無憂先計劃生育。而家個心好亂，<br />\n老婆要我賣一架車，只准Keep 四架，又話個仔未出世已經要洗我一球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf364299d36c35cd92ead5742698799dffc8b33","tid":883284,"uid":218575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T17:10:00.000Z","msg":"送架俾我 唔洗煩"},{"pid":"3c5fdb1bbe97902509f9ec1989c9f59a45371f0f","tid":883284,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T17:10:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12cc0731e4bff33b4c5ee231bff1bdbd3ca7bc5","tid":883284,"uid":59192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T17:10:59.000Z","msg":"關我地撚事"},{"pid":"a33e4509469bdf91f9f28fcdf620d74f2a4100c3","tid":883284,"uid":198583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T17:11:26.000Z","msg":"吓？你個BB冇右㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a207adeeaeac5a7b1a8e069a6ae9c36ccafd865","tid":883284,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a33e4509469bdf91f9f28fcdf620d74f2a4100c3","tid":883284,"uid":198583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T17:11:26.000Z","msg":"吓？你個BB冇右㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cit